{"id":771,"date":"2026-02-03T08:14:38","date_gmt":"2026-02-03T08:14:38","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tanyanggu.com\/?p=771"},"modified":"2026-02-03T08:34:57","modified_gmt":"2026-02-03T08:34:57","slug":"771-2","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/tanyanggu.com\/771-2\/","title":{"rendered":"Emergent Cosmos"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<div class=\"ast-oembed-container \" style=\"height: 100%;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"EmergentCosmos\uff08\u56fd\u969b\u79d1\u5b66\u6620\u50cf\u796d\u7b2c14\u56de\u30c9\u30fc\u30e0\u30d5\u30a7\u30b9\u30bf\u7248\uff09\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/IaivLU6E4Is?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe><\/div>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">\u300cEmergent Cosmos\u300d\u306f\u3001\u6642\u9593\u3068\u5b58\u5728\u306e\u91cd\u306a\u308a\u3092\u56db\u6b21\u5143\u7684\u8996\u70b9\u304b\u3089\u63cf\u304d\u51fa\u3059\u4f5c\u54c1\u3067\u3042\u308b\u3002\u6d41\u52d5\u3059\u308b\u5149\u306e\u4e2d\u306b\u6d6e\u304b\u3076\u767d\u3044\u69cb\u9020\u4f53\u306f\u3001\u6642\u9593\u305d\u306e\u3082\u306e\u3092\u53ef\u8996\u5316\u3057\u3001\u904b\u52d5\u306e\u8ecc\u8de1\u3092\u591a\u5c64\u7684\u306b\u523b\u3080\u3002\u305d\u3053\u306b\u306f\u8907\u6570\u306e\u5e73\u884c\u5b87\u5b99\u306b\u304a\u3051\u308b\u300c\u81ea\u5df1\u300d\u306e\u59ff\u304c\u91cd\u306a\u308a\u5408\u3044\u3001\u7570\u306a\u308b\u4e16\u754c\u304c\u5171\u9cf4\u3057\u5408\u3046\u77ac\u9593\u304c\u793a\u3055\u308c\u3066\u3044\u308b\u3002<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"> &#8220;Emergent  Cosmos&#8221; explores the intersection of time and existence from a 4D perspective. In a sea of fluid light, floating white structures visualize time, recording the multi-layered paths of movement. It reveals the overlapping &#8220;selves&#8221; of parallel universes\u2014a singular moment where different worlds find their resonance. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">\u4e0a\u6620\uff1a<br>2025.08 \u2013 \u306a\u304b\u306eZERO\u30e1\u30c7\u30a3\u30a2\u82b8\u8853\u30d7\u30ed\u30b0\u30e9\u30e02025. \u6771\u4eac. \u65e5\u672c<br>2025.10 \u2013 \u56fd\u969b\u79d1\u5b66\u6620\u50cf\u796d\u7b2c14\u56de\u30c9\u30fc\u30e0\u30d5\u30a7\u30b9\u30bf. \u6771\u4eac. \u65e5\u672c <br>2025.12 \u2013 Ghost in the Mirror \u2013 Screening&amp;Exhibition of Visual Anthropological Works. \u4e0a\u6d77. \u4e2d\u56fd<br><br>Director: RustyHead(Tan Yanggu) <br>Music: First Floor &#8211; DNS<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"http:\/\/tanyanggu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/IMG_9657444.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-781\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1992\" height=\"1328\" src=\"http:\/\/tanyanggu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/IMG_9656.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-773\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1992\" height=\"1328\" src=\"http:\/\/tanyanggu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/MG_9460.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-774\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"http:\/\/tanyanggu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/\u30bf\u30f3\u30e4\u30f3\u30b0\uff3fsub_02.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-775\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"http:\/\/tanyanggu.com\/wp-co